106
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,870
You still remember.

107
00:06:28,310 --> 00:06:29,800
You must keep your word.

108
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:32,240
Let's go!

109
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:35,950
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

110
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:41,340
