111
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,630
-Come on, Fu!
-Come on, Fu!

112
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:42,720
Fu, go!

113
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:44,830
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

114
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,659
-Fu!
-Fu!

115
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,159
Go, go!

116
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:48,070
